org.eclipse.viatra.emf.runtime.modelmanipulation

Class AbstractModelManipulations

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.viatra.emf.runtime.modelmanipulation.AbstractModelManipulations
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IModelManipulations
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ModelManipulationWithEditingDomain, SimpleModelManipulations

    public abstract class AbstractModelManipulations
extends java.lang.Object
implements IModelManipulations
    Abstract base class for model manipulation implementation. It checks for the preconditions of the operations, and the subclasses should override the do* methods.
    Author:
    Zoltan Ujhelyi
